title: Production of creamery butter in Canada 2019
summary: The graph shows the Production of creamery in Tonnes Canada during 2019 .
There are several peaks and dips throughout the year .
The maximum value of Production has been recorded for September , and the minimum value has been recorded for August .
gold: The line chart provides an overview of the production of creamery butter in Canada in 2019 . The production generally drops from January to August except for a gentle rise in April and reaches its minimum in August at around 7000 tonnes . It then grows from August to December .
